                            <comment id="13555811" author="ralph.goers@dslextreme.com" created="Thu, 17 Jan 2013 03:39:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I added PropsUtil to the API.  It should be renamed to PropertiesUtil and the one in core removed. The one in the API allows a properties file to be provided to provide default values for the properties.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
